{"entity":{"id":"rec4fFrtrUuDVkTNK","type":"event","slug":"event-329","label":"Peter meets Cornelius","subtitle":"AD 38","count":33,"description":"","rawId":"rec4fFrtrUuDVkTNK"},"stats":{"verses":33,"participants":4,"locations":2},"nodes":[{"id":"rec4fFrtrUuDVkTNK","type":"event","group":"focus","label":"Peter meets Cornelius","slug":"event-329","score":33},{"id":"reco82mzy0XTzaOgv","type":"person","group":"person","label":"Holy Spirit","slug":"holy_spirit_7400","score":246},{"id":"recTa6EpjvdBbC1Uk","type":"person","group":"person","label":"Simon the Tanner","slug":"simon_2753","score":4},{"id":"recX9MMADoVI2CSP1","type":"person","group":"person","label":"Simon Peter","slug":"peter_2745","score":175},{"id":"recq0lOFoVY6zUYkV","type":"person","group":"person","label":"Cornelius","slug":"cornelius_956","score":10},{"id":"recIeuZZMsolnZA6n","type":"place","group":"place","label":"Joppa","slug":"joppa_652","score":14},{"id":"recKrSp5YmwkgRKv0","type":"place","group":"place","label":"Caesarea","slug":"caesarea_266","score":16},{"id":"recxH9n2Xk1PM6DvB","type":"event","group":"event","label":"Peter heals Aeneas and Dorcas","slug":"event-328","score":5}],"links":[{"source":"rec4fFrtrUuDVkTNK","target":"reco82mzy0XTzaOgv","label":"participant"},{"source":"rec4fFrtrUuDVkTNK","target":"recTa6EpjvdBbC1Uk","label":"participant"},{"source":"rec4fFrtrUuDVkTNK","target":"recX9MMADoVI2CSP1","label":"participant"},{"source":"rec4fFrtrUuDVkTNK","target":"recq0lOFoVY6zUYkV","label":"participant"},{"source":"rec4fFrtrUuDVkTNK","target":"recIeuZZMsolnZA6n","label":"location"},{"source":"rec4fFrtrUuDVkTNK","target":"recKrSp5YmwkgRKv0","label":"location"},{"source":"rec4fFrtrUuDVkTNK","target":"recxH9n2Xk1PM6DvB","label":"predecessor"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec0H0i7vksC81oxw","ref":"Acts.10.1","text":"There was a certain man in Caesarea called Cornelius, a centurion of the band called the Italian band,","year":41},{"id":"recy9ixaff2aOdPi0","ref":"Acts.10.2","text":"A devout man, and one that feared God with all his house, which gave much alms to the people, and prayed to God alway.","year":41},{"id":"recxhk4HgMo9Dc31u","ref":"Acts.10.3","text":"He saw in a vision evidently about the ninth hour of the day an angel of God coming in to him, and saying unto him, Cornelius.","year":41},{"id":"recUIL4jC0YKa6nnW","ref":"Acts.10.4","text":"And when he looked on him, he was afraid, and said, What is it, Lord? And he said unto him, Thy prayers and thine alms are come up for a memorial before God.","year":41},{"id":"rec0a4e9yxmK9EuYS","ref":"Acts.10.5","text":"And now send men to Joppa, and call for one Simon, whose surname is Peter:","year":41},{"id":"rec7RMRsAJ333VlwT","ref":"Acts.10.6","text":"He lodgeth with one Simon a tanner, whose house is by the sea side: he shall tell thee what thou oughtest to do.","year":41},{"id":"rec7BBWiFEGpXYqlW","ref":"Acts.10.7","text":"And when the angel which spake unto Cornelius was departed, he called two of his household servants, and a devout soldier of them that waited on him continually;","year":41},{"id":"recCrSzaaY49ios6y","ref":"Acts.10.8","text":"And when he had declared all these things unto them, he sent them to Joppa.","year":41}]}
